  { :name => "W Atlanta Midtown's 5th Annual Halloween Bash: A Night In The Living Dead Room & ~VINTAGE~ Horror Picture Show.", :longitude => -84.381545, :latitude => 33.786674, :gmaps => true, :description => "========================================\nFOR TICKETS, PLEASE VISIT http://www.halloweenbashatl.com\n========================================\n\nGerber Group and Wil May+MAKESHIFT's #COOL bring you a two level, double feature of tricks and treats with W Atlanta Midtown's 5th Annual Halloween Bash on Saturday, October 27th, 2012. \n\nOn the lobby level, prepare and beware for A Night In The Living Dead Room. Not feeling like yourself? Have a shot, bite the lime and become a tequila zombie. ARRRRGH!\n\nUpstairs in Whiskey Park, we present the ~VINTAGE~ Horror Picture Show, a special edition of our regularly scheduled VINTAGE Saturdays. Dress up, get down and stay alive as Atlanta's most evil genius DJs revive magical gems from the past with the most raging tracks from now. Get your bones shakin' and rattin'... or else, we will.\n\nWill it be whiskey or full moonshine? Pick your poison, as our devilishly pretty bar staff concocts handcrafted, body numbing potions and elixirs. Scream but don't be scared. Bahahahaha. Get out and check in at the 5th Annual W Atlanta Midtown Halloween Bash: A Special 2 Level Event.\n\n========================================\nFOR TICKETS, PLEASE VISIT http://www.halloweenbashatl.com\n========================================\n\nCorpse reviver spinning in the Living Room\n*****  DJ EU \"Ke Es La Ke\"  *****\nhttp://www.facebook.com/DJEUKSLKFB\nEDM, House, Electro, Latin, Open Format\n\n~VINTAGE~ Resident spinning in Whiskey Park\n*****  DJ Dibiase \"The Million Dollar DJ\"  *****\nhttp://www.facebook.com/djdibiase\nRock 'n Roll, Soul, Oldies, Hip-Hop, Pop, and Top 40's\n\n========================================\nFOR TICKETS, PLEASE VISIT http://www.halloweenbashatl.com\n========================================", :start_time => "2012-10-27 21:00:00", :end_time => "2012-10-28 04:00:00", :address => "188 14th St NW, Atlanta, GA 30318, USA", :fb_id => 395616240512341, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/276833_395616240512341_2084141546_q.jpg", :atenders => 0, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-10-25 14:27:28", :updated_at => "2012-10-25 14:27:28" },
  { :name => "BeltLine walk from Inman Marta Station to the West End Marta Station.", :longitude => -84.3528121, :latitude => 33.7576331, :gmaps => true, :description => "www.indiegogo.com/angelshouse\n\nAtlanta, we had 60 people come out to walk the BeltLine to King of Pops.  What a great walk. Check out the pictures here.\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.10100345850000749.2412671.12803415&type=1 \n\nThe next walk will be this Saturday starting at 10am at the Inman Park Marta station walking to the West End Marta Station. The route:\n\nhttp://www.bikely.com/maps/bike-path/South-Side-Beltline-Walk\n\nThe details for this walk on Saturday, Oct 27, 2012.\n \nEveryone is welcome, starting at the Inman Park Marta Station (north side of station) at 10am we will walk to the West End Marta station 6 1/2 miles. The walk will take place on 1 1/2 miles of city streets, 4 1/4 miles of barely active rail, 1/4 mile of overgrown corridor, 1/2 mile of city streets.\n\nWe'll be walking through my back yard and I'll be giving a short tour of the house in it's pre-construction state.  \n\nAfter we're done with the walk on the BeltLine you'll be able to take Marta to get back to the Inman Park Marta Station or where ever you need to go.\n\nStrollers will be a problem on this walk but dogs and kids are welcome.  \n\nI'm planing on walking next weekend as well, West End to Bankhead on the 4th of November, Sunday at 10am\n\nThe walks will always be free but I am asking everyone to share the link to the indiegogo fund raiser I have going at the moment to raise money for my house.\n\nCheck it out here.\n\nwww.indiegogo.com/angelshouse\n\nThank you.\n\nSee you on the BeltLine \n\n\n\n\n\n", :start_time => "2012-10-27 11:00:00", :end_time => "2012-10-27 14:00:00", :address => "1055 DeKalb Ave NE, Atlanta, GA 30307, USA", :fb_id => 312675392172720, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/372925_312675392172720_2134309186_q.jpg", :atenders => 146, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-10-25 14:27:30", :updated_at => "2012-10-25 14:27:30" },
