  { :name => "Recolección de firmas por un Circo sin Animales", :longitude => -70.65046219999999, :latitude => -33.4395876, :gmaps => true, :description => "Animanaturalis conoce la triste y cruda realidad en la cual están sometidos miles de animales a raíz del cautiverio y sufrimiento que les provoca ser usados y entrenados para shows y espectáculos circenses, siendo privados de sus derechos de vivir libres en su habitat natural. AnimaNaturalis \n\nLa campaña tiene por objetivo lograr la promulgación de un proyecto de ley que actualmente se encuentra en el Congreso Nacional, y que prohíbe a lo largo y ancho de nuestro territorio la existencia de circos que utilicen animales en sus espectáculos.\n\nTu apoyo será primordial, pues mientras mayor sea la cantidad de firmas que registremos en esta campaña, más cerca estaremos del objetivo, y por que no decirlo, de un mundo un poco más justo.\n\n¡Te invitamos a partipar en esta jornada de recolección y a firmar virtualmente en el siguiente link: http://www.animanaturalis.org/n/36509/firma_por_un_circo_sin_animales\n\n", :start_time => "2012-10-25 14:00:00", :end_time => "2012-10-25 17:00:00", :address => "Huérfanos 898-1004, Santiago, Santiago Metropolitan Region, Chile", :fb_id => 238551052939604, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/276548_238551052939604_998420536_q.jpg", :atenders => 141, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-10-25 15:04:56", :updated_at => "2012-10-25 15:04:56" },
  { :name => "::DANCE OF THE DEAD II::FEDDE LE GRAND::", :longitude => -82.3277389, :latitude => 29.6520142, :gmaps => true, :description => "Committee Entertainment and The Dynasty Group\nIn association with Student Government Productions\nPresent: DANCE OF THE DEAD II with FEDDE LE GRAND\n\nIt's not easy redefining what a holiday means, particularly one as beloved and cherished as HALLOWEEN. But when you combine all the great elements Halloween has to offer, first and foremost among them the unbelievable vibe and energy it brings, and you pair it with one of the very best DJ's in the world and an unbelievable production, you create something so powerful and transformative you create a new meaning for what is already many people's favorite holiday. Last year, that meant bringing you AVICII. This year, we bring you another legend in dance music...FEDDE LE GRAND.\n\nThe hits (\"Metrum\", \"So Much Love\", \"Put Your Hands up for Detroit\", \"Autosave\", \"Paradise\", \"So Much Love\") are only equaled by the fantastic live presence and unbridled skill Fedde Le Grand brings to the table. Ranked consistently as one of the top Dj's alive and destroyer of Main Stages such as Tomorrowland and Ultra alike, this will be a set for the ages. Bring out your best costumes and come prepared for DANCE OF THE DEAD II. \n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nTICKET UPDATE:\n\nOn THURSDAY (Oct 25, 2012), we will be in Turlington Plaza from noon until 4:00 pm (or until tickets sell out), selling the remaining Student Discount Tickets, and then the Non Discounted GA Tickets which will start @ $43 and go up from there.\n\nAttention UF Students:  Thanks to SGP, you will each have the opportunity to buy a discounted ticket by showing your Gator 1 ID. The discounted Student Ticket price will increase as the show gets closer to selling out, so please arrive as early as possible to receive the cheapest price.\n\nThere will be two (2) discounted tickets given per Gator 1 ID, and you can bring up to five (5) Gator 1 IDs if you would like to pick up tickets for your friends. \n\n***Discounted Student Tickets will be available strictly on a first come, first served basis. Supplies are extremely limited so please plan accordingly.\n\n***If you prefer to buy your tickets online, Non Discounted GA Tickets are available here for your convenience:  http://feddegville.eventbrite.com/\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nThe Vault has played host to Porter Robinson, Alesso, Madeon, Zedd in 2012 alone, will be transformed with a massive production of lights, sound and decor to make this a total body Halloween experience. \n\nThis event is brought to you by Committee Entertainment and The Dynasty Group, in association with Student Government Productions. \n\nOFFICIAL OPENERS:\nAdrian Villaverde \nLuccio \n\nFor more info on this event:\nhttp://www.facebook.com/TheDynastyGroup\n\n\nFor more info on Fedde Le Grand:\nhttp://www.feddelegrand.com/\nhttp://www.youtube.com/feddelegrand\nhttp://twitter.com/FeddeLeGrand\nhttp://www.myspace.com/djfeddelegrand\nhttp://feddelegrand.hyves.nl/\nhttp://gplus.to/feddelegrand\n\nFor ticket info, please call or text:\nJustin 352.214.9324\nAntonio 352.870.2185\nLuijo 352.359.8129 \n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nFEDDE LE GRAND FULL 2012 ULTRA SET\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NJtOKFrEODQ\n\n\"Put Your Hands Up For Detroit\"\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYs2HHYqmxw\n\"So Much Love\"\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JBhBbxm4nak\nColdplay \"Paradise\" FLG Remix\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gQA5gQQNkIo\n\"Let Me Think About It\" ft. Ida Corr\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=19WUwZYM7bM\n\"Autosave\"\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_jG9yGiq_rs\n\"Praise You\" Remix\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kBUXNz-GoYw\n", :start_time => "2012-10-30 22:00:00", :end_time =