  { :name => "Planeta No y Julia Smith - Sala Andes Concepción", :longitude => -73.0449323, :latitude => -36.8256041, :gmaps => true, :description => "Luego de tocar con regularidad durante más de un año y después de la exitosa presentación en el Conce y Rock,  la banda santiaguina Planeta No vuelve a Concepción a presentar parte del material que compondrá su disco debut, producido por Alex Anwandter y que está agendado para el primer semestre del 2013.\n\nJunto con ello se presentarán los penquistas de Julia Smith quienes presentarán un show como parte de la promoción de su primer disco \"Hagamos las Maletas y Vámonos del Planeta\", editado este 2012 bajo el sello Beast Discos. Además darán una adelanto del próximo Ep el cual ya están trabajando. \n\nLugar: Sala Andes\nHora: 19.00 \nENTRADA LIBERADA\n\nEscúchalos en : \n\nhttp://soundcloud.com/planetano\nhttp://soundcloud.com/juliasmith\n\n\nColaboran:\nCámara Chilena de la Construcción\nCaja Los Andes\nBufón Group\n\n\n\n\n", :start_time => "2012-10-26 19:00:00", :end_time => "2012-10-26 21:30:00", :address => "Bernardo O'Higgins 1026-1096, Concepción, Biobío Region, Chile", :fb_id => 481062581915152, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/373036_481062581915152_1124288242_q.jpg", :atenders => 211, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-10-25 15:07:50", :updated_at => "2012-10-25 15:07:50" },
  { :name => "Milk:Presents...SCARED SHITLESS!", :longitude => -2.9760414, :latitude => 53.4019902, :gmaps => true, :description => "Milk:Presents...SCARED SHITLESS The Jimmy Saville Seance.\n\nOnce you've received the delights of the Woodland Social, https://www.facebook.com/events/339348426161354/\n\nGet your most insane halloween attire, venture to an offy and stock up to the hilt! \n\nYour in for sick one! With a live DJ Set from the Soul of Jimmy 'THE BASTARD' Saville himself!!!\n\nAs always we'll be confirming our acts up until the final hour! So keep your eyes peeled for the announcements!\n\nWONDERLUST!\nBROKEN MEN!\nMERRYGO!\n\nIt's also the celebration of a very special birthday!\n\n£5 OTD BYOB\nOfficial Doors 11pm \nbut come down whenever you want!\n\n\n\n\n\n\n", :start_time => "2012-10-26 19:00:00", :end_time => "2012-10-26 22:00:00", :address => "116 Bold St, Chinatown, Liverpool, Merseyside L1, UK", :fb_id => 428789370508535, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-snc6/592209_428789370508535_274875040_q.jpg", :atenders => 65, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-10-25 15:07:52", :updated_at => "2012-10-25 15:07:52" },
  { :name => "The Fire Beneath the Sea hit the Wirral again", :longitude => -3.1333718, :latitude => 53.4043234, :gmaps => true, :description => "Wirralites - do you remember the giddy days of July, when a bunch of hat wearing insane rappers descended on you at 7.30 on a Saturday night at Glassfire during The Festival of Firsts. Well, I do and it was pure sick. \n\nLiverpudlians - many of you came over and had a great time. Do it again if you fancy a change of scene on a Friday night though I have to concede the last train back over the water is at 11pm...\n\nSince that gig, clip attached for memory's sake we have morphed into a full-on live band with a fat brass section, keyboards, drums, guitar,bass, DJ and usually around 6 rappers. Real momentum is growing, as we've recently gigged at Kung-Fu hip hop night at The Attic at Matthew Street and headlined at The Kazimier, which was awesome. The gigs are coming in thick and fast, and we're really excited to be playing at Glassfire again.\n\nThe summer live line-up\n\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GS-aYlMQxwk\n\n\nThe fatter sound that's going off now\n\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ig-C611hVrI\n\nAll I can say is GET TO THIS as its truly spectacular.\n\n\n\n", :start_time => "2012-10-26 16:30:00", :end_time => "2012-10-26 19:30:00", :address => "214 Millhouse Ln, Birkenhead, Wirral CH46, UK", :fb_id => 271023403001180, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/373081_271023403001180_1247603693_q.jpg", :atenders => 26, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-10-25 15:07:54", :updated_at => "2012-10-25 15:07:54" },
